# Title: Windows Firewall Profile Disabled
# Author: Austin Songer @austinsonger
# Date: 2021-10-12
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects when a user disables the Windows Firewall via a Profile to help evade defense.
# MITRE Tactic: Defense Evasion
# Tags: attack.defense-evasion, attack.t1562.004
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/powershell/powershell_script/posh_ps_windows_firewall_profile_disabled.yml

ScriptBlockText="*Set-NetFirewallProfile *" ScriptBlockText="* -Enabled *" ScriptBlockText="* False*" ScriptBlockText IN ("* -All *", "*Public*", "*Domain*", "*Private*")